name: PRuntime v2.2.0
body:
## What's Changed
* Upgrade to Polkadot v1.0.0 by @jasl in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1363
* pink-runtime: Change storage depoist min mask size to 256 by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1382
* pink-runtime: Fix tokio runtime missing in unittest by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1392
* prpc: Add system contract and so on by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1390
* pruntime: Detect checkpoint breaking changes in unittest by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1381
* pink-runtime: Replace DispatchError::Other with concrete errors by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1384
* Upgrade to Polkadot v1.1.0 by @jasl in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1403
* Fix clippy warnings in contracts by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1409
* Remove the precompiled build tool `crate-version` by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1418
* Add capability to build DCAP pruntime by @jasl in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1429
* PRuntime: Support generate DCAP artifact by @jasl in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1430
* Update rocket to 0.5.0 by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1441
* pruntime: Show authority set change in log by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1447
* pruntime: Sign the event block and dump runtime metadata by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1423
* DCAP support by @jasl in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1443
* pruntime: Reject old version of checkpoint by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1368
* pruntime: Sidevm incoming HTTP stream via pRuntime RPC by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1366
* pruntime: Support for deploy sidevm to selected workers. by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1399
* pruntime: Support for query between sidevm and pink by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1398
* Sidevm as pink `js_eval` engine by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1450
* Add some doc comments for pink runtime by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1462
* pruntime: Fix incorrect code_hash in prpc::GetContractInfo by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1464
* sidevm: Remove the 512 bytes chunk size limit by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1467
* pink-runtime: Disable code lockup deposit by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1477
* unittest: Human readable type tree snapshot by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1475
* sidevm: Use trust-dns as DNS resolver by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1479
* pruntime: Add origin in event block by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1478
* Read the validator set from `Grandpa::Authorities` as a fallback by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1484
* pruntime: Fix possible mis-update last_header on error by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1487
* Correct DCAP constants by @jasl in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1488
* pink runtime: Increase gas limit to 5x by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1501
* pruntime: Address mapping from H160 in query by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1495
* phactory: read authority set change from header by @nanometerzhu in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1508
* 95% test coverage for pink-runtime by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1522
* pruntime: Implement dcap key handover by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1524
* pink: Add chain extension to get RA report by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1527
* Move the prpc proto files back from external repo by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1537
* pRuntime v2.2.0 by @kvinwang in https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/pull/1540

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Phala-Network/phala-blockchain/compare/pruntime-v2.1.0...pruntime-v2.2.0
